snippet.title: Ben Affleck has been spotted. At the movie theatre, I had an intense talk with Lily Rabe,
snippet.description:
Ben Affleck has been spotted. At the movie theatre, I had an intense talk with Lily Rabe,

#jenniferlopez #benaffleck

On Sunday, Ben Affleck was seen having an animated conversation with Lily Rabe, his co-star in The Tender Bar, and it appeared like he had a lot on his mind. The 49-year-old actor was seen gesticulating forcefully during a talk with the American Horror Story star, 39, at the Landmark Theatre in Los Angeles. During the conversation, Lily was observed carefully listening with a concerned expression on her face, however, it was unclear what the topic was. Throughout, Ben appeared agitated.
